data.description: Discover this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom single-family home nestled in desirable Deerfield Beach, FL.  Spacious open floor plan with updated kitchen, quartz island, impact windows, and  stainless steel appliances. Relax or entertain in the spacious fenced backyard. No HOA restrictions. Conveniently located near the beach, shopping centers, and dining options, this property offers the quintessential South Florida lifestyle. The third bedroom features an independent entrance, offering versatility as an efficiency unit. Experience modern comfort and convenience in this prime location!
